                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 200.11L44/14 and 15.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams—Paraphrases.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">San José</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-07-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 17, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Lawson arrested today. The Minister for Foreign Affairs tells me that he will be
                    deported for Galveston on the 18th instant.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Langhorne</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
